{"data": [{"id": "4745420", "title": "Vestas Shares At Multi-Year Lows While Headwinds Shift To Tailwinds - Trading Buy Update", "description": "<p><b><i>Vestas Wind Systems A/S </i></b><em><strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VWDRY\" title=\"Vestas Wind Systems A/S\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:VWDRY</a>) Z4 Research Quick Update </strong></em></p> <p>We've written on global wind turbine sales and service player Vestas a number of times over the years, but not recently. Over the last several years the wind space has been a scene of widespread stock price carnage. This really started with Covid where timelines became stretched as material and transportation costs skyrocketed impacting orders, revenues, and margins and necessitating big changes to the supply chain. This was then followed by a globally higher interest rate environment bringing into doubt project economics, policy uncertainty, some pretty high-profile warranty issues, and projecting permitting woes. The most recent nail in the narrative: President-Elect Trump was reelected. And renewables shares everywhere legged lower.</p> <p>Keeping all that in mind, here's a key point timeline:</p> <ul> <li>2018 EBIT margins were ~10%.</li> <li>2019 to 2021 saw margins decline annually. The saving grace of those years was the Service segment. Vestas manages wind turbines around the world under long-term contracts and these are generally 2 to 3x that of selling a turbine. In this period, service margins were 26% pre-COVID and still 24% by 2021. Unfortunately, the Service segment was relatively small then and overall margins fell sharply during the period.</li> <li>In 2022 turbine and overall margins went negative despite Service margin resilience. This was the trough year for margins as management put in place better costing procedures.</li> </ul> <p><strong>This brings us to the present day and 2024 is expected to be essentially flat to 2023 but with improved margins. </strong>Revenues moved up on higher volumes and pricing. Turbine margins began to recover Overall margins were impacted by a non-cash charge for the service side to adjust for planned costs going forward.</p> <p><strong>Looking ahead, 2025 is expected to be a better year:</strong></p> <p>Revenue is currently expected to be up</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745420-vestas-shares-at-multi-year-lows-while-headwinds-shift-to-tailwinds-trading-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 23:34:55"}, {"id": "4745419", "title": "Allot Stock: Potential Verizon Expansion Validates The Bull Case", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cyber security and safety concept. Digital protection from viruses and malware. Modern futuristic technology background. 3D render\" data-id=\"1500027975\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"807px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500027975/image_1500027975.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) c