/p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The Fed's hawkish turn</h2> <p>The S&amp;P500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>) fell sharply by 2.95% after the Fed's December meeting interest rate decision announcement, and Powell's press conference.</p> <p>The Fed made a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740169-sp500-expect-the-feds-major-hawkish-turn-in-december\">hawkish turn</a> - it likely made the last</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745413-s-and-p500-buy-the-dip-or-expect-a-deeper-sell-off", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 23:01:11"}, {"id": "4745411", "title": "MAGS: The Strong Concentration In Mag 7 And Its Challenges", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up hand scrolling on a digital tablet at night\" data-id=\"1633826824\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826824.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1633826824/image_1633826