te Complex Patterns on a Wafer during Semiconductor and Computer Chip Production at Fab or Foundry.\" data-id=\"1468266081\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SweetBunFactory</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Applied Materials (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMAT\" class=\"ticker-link\">AMAT</a>), the maker of semiconductor WFE, or Wafer Fabrication Equipment, has experienced a phenomenal few years where fabrication companies doubled down on purchasing more fabrication equipment to cope with the elevated demand for chips being</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468266081/image_1468266081.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745403-applied-materials-stock-in-2025-cloudy-with-chance-of-windfalls", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 22:36:20"}, {"id": "4745400", "title": "LTC Properties: Steady Growth Set To Continue In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Model house on calculator with stack of coins money on natural green background, Calculating interest payments and Property tax concept\" data-id=\"1454987355\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MonthiraYodtiwong</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>LTC Properties, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LTC\" title=\"LTC Properties, Inc.\">LTC</a></span>) has significantly outperformed the Vanguard Real Estate Index Fund ETF Shares (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) so far in 2024, delivering a ~17% gain against the ~3% total return for the broad US REIT ETF:</p> <p></p> <p>I believe</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1454987355/image_1454987355.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745400-ltc-properties-reit-steady-growth-to-continue-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 22:30:09"}, {"id": "4745397", "title": "Nestle: Sluggish Business Leaves Shares Looking Cheap", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Nespresso coffee store on Champs-Elysees Avenue\" data-id=\"1203760355\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1203760355/image_1203760355.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: